    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言解雇特别顾问；碧昂斯将与哈里斯联手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/trump-vows-to-fire-special-counsel-beyonce-to-rally-with-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普誓言，如果特别顾问杰克·史密斯重返白宫，他将解雇他，因为他希望在西部摇摆州的闪电战之前动员自己的支持者，目前几个战场州已经开始提前投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/trump-vows-to-fire-special-counsel-beyonce-to-rally-with-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 15:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>碧昂丝将与卡马拉·哈里斯联手，提升她的名人支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/beyonce-to-rally-with-kamala-harris-boosting-her-celebrity-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[流行音乐巨星碧昂丝·诺尔斯-卡特 (Beyoncé Knowles-Carter) 将于周五与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 一起竞选，这位将自己标榜为赋权象征的艺术家将为寻求成为第一位赢得总统大选的黑人女性的候选人提供支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/beyonce-to-rally-with-kamala-harris-boosting-her-celebrity-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 15:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统鲁托为激起全国愤怒的阿达尼投资进行辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/kenya-s-ruto-defends-adani-investment-that-stoked-nation-s-anger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托支持政府接受阿达尼集团私人资本的决定，但由于部分交易的不透明性，该决定引发了抗议并激怒了公众。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/kenya-s-ruto-defends-adani-investment-that-stoked-nation-s-anger</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 15:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和以色列称加沙停火谈判代表将于下周举行会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/us-and-israel-say-gaza-cease-fire-negotiators-to-meet-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国和以色列称，以色列和哈马斯谈判人员将在未来几天举行会晤，重新努力结束加沙地带的灾难性冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/us-and-israel-say-gaza-cease-fire-negotiators-to-meet-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 15:01:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>支持率暴跌后特鲁多改变移民政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/trudeau-reverses-course-on-immigration-after-support-plunges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于创纪录的移民流入导致公众对移民的支持度下降，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 不再欢迎新移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/trudeau-reverses-course-on-immigration-after-support-plunges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 14:36:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克执政党赢得选举，但选举结果受到欺诈指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/mozambique-s-ruling-party-wins-vote-tainted-by-fraud-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克执政党候选人以压倒性优势赢得总统选举，而欺诈指控引发的紧张局势让这个东南部非洲国家陷入紧张之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/mozambique-s-ruling-party-wins-vote-tainted-by-fraud-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 14:27:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯表示英国财政规则变化将增加投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/reeves-says-uk-fiscal-rule-change-will-increase-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯证实，她将对财政规则进行调整，允许更多借贷用于投资，以促进新工党政府促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/reeves-says-uk-fiscal-rule-change-will-increase-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 13:39:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>到 2028 年，德国税收收入将减少 126 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/germany-sees-12-6-billion-less-in-tax-income-by-2028-on-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲最大经济体德国经济增长举步维艰，德国联邦政府预计，截至 2028 年的五年内，德国税收收入将比 5 月份的预测减少 126 亿欧元（合 136 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/germany-sees-12-6-billion-less-in-tax-income-by-2028-on-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 13:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利第二轮民意调查中奥尔班领导的政党失去领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/orban-s-party-loses-lead-in-second-opinion-poll-in-hungary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 的政党在几天内进行的第二份民意调查中落后于其新晋挑战者彼得·马加尔 (Peter Magyar) 的政党，这表明 2026 年的议会选举可能会非常激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/orban-s-party-loses-lead-in-second-opinion-poll-in-hungary</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫敦促各机构将人工智能用于军事和间谍用途</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/white-house-pushes-agencies-to-adopt-ai-for-military-spy-uses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的国家安全备忘录，拜登政府表示，美国必须加快将人工智能用于军事和情报用途，指示各机构以安全的方式迅速部署最强大的系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/white-house-pushes-agencies-to-adopt-ai-for-military-spy-uses</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
